Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:03.17,Song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(30,0)}nannen tatte mo boku wa shinanai kibouron bakari o tonaeteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:06.00,Song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(30,0)}touzen kyou mo kimi wa inai no ni sa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:12.30,Song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(30,0)}"kamawanai, shine yo, shine yo" tte tekubi o nigitte tada norotte
